= Verdict Debate Pattern =

{{info}}
**Developer Reference** — The structured multi-step LLM debate process used in Stage 4 of the ClaimAssessmentBoundary (CB) pipeline to produce high-quality, balanced verdicts.

**Key Files**: ##apps/web/src/lib/analyzer/verdict-stage.ts##, ##apps/web/prompts/claimboundary.prompt.md##
{{/info}}

== 🎯 Overview ==

FactHarbor replaces simple LLM "zero-shot" adjudication with a structured **5-step adversarial debate pattern**. This design ensures that every verdict is stress-tested by a dedicated "challenger" role before being finalized, significantly reducing the risk of stable model bias and "echo-chamber" reasoning.

{{mermaid}}
